original: Zetterberg, Gunnar Lennart, civilingenjör, Göteborg, f. 16/6/10 i Sthlm av byggn :ing. Carl Z. o. Maria Johansson. G. 41 m. Dagmar Lindgren. Barn: Ulf f. 43, Wilhelm 46. — Studrex. v. Lundsbergs sk. 29, stud. v. KTH (V) 30-34. Anst. v. väging:kont. i Östersund 34-35, v. Byggn .-firma Zetterberg A-B i Sthlm 35-38, chef f. avd:kont. i Gbg sed. 38. Löjtn. VVK 41, kapten 46.
translated: Zetterberg, Gunnar Lennart, civil engineer, Gothenburg, b. June 16, 1910 in Stockholm to building engineer Carl Z. and Maria Johansson. Married in 1941 to Dagmar Lindgren. Children: Ulf, b. 1943, Wilhelm, b. 1946. Attended Lundsbergs School until 1929, studied at Royal Institute of Technology (V) from 1930 to 1934. Employed at a road construction office in Östersund from 1934 to 1935, at building company Zetterberg A-B in Stockholm from 1935 to 1938, and as department head at an office in Gothenburg since 1938. Lieutenant in the Swedish Volunteer Corps in 1941, captain in 1946.
